{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where you are not-- before the war, people that did not have the facilities at home could wash themselves in-- in sinks and with water or go to special bath houses.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like a lot of people, at least once a week, they went to the hot baths and the steam baths or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these were not the circumstances in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And besides--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The best they could under the circumstances, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you were-- were 10 people to a small apartment, and some of them weren't even related, you don't free-- feel free to undress yourself and-- and wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't get the privacy or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they just-- it was a lot of superficial, the best under the circumstances.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the washing facility of clothes weren't sufficient.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the worst part was there wasn't any fresh fruit and vegetable sufficient.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing sufficient.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were, in our ghetto, a lot of civilian Germans lived around my home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, civilian Germans are people with a German background that lived in Poland and still kept their culture and their-- they were not Catholics.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] evangelicals and so on or Protestants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they kept their culture, and they were like the Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were Germans in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when the Germans occupied my hometown, they all became big shots. 12-Year-old [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] children of the volksdeutchen-- they were called volksdeutchen-- were belonging to Hitler jungen, and they were given guns, and they used to target shoot into the ghetto just to practice their shooting.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And people got really killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were falling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In fact, one of my close girlfriends was tied to a pole, and-- and they were target shooting to her.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
